<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-2073] Memory leak on zookeeper_close</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-2073</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running valgrind against a zookeeper client using the C API, I noticed an occasional memory leak on zookeeper_close.  I traced the issue to a regression added by fix &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-804&quot; title=&quot;c unit tests failing due to &amp;quot;assertion cptr failed&amp;quot;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;ZOOKEEPER-804&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;ZOOKEEPER-804&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.  The attached patch fixes the regression and the associated memory leak.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12752768">ZOOKEEPER-2073</key>
            <summary>Memory leak on zookeeper_close</summary>
